  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>Traveler</u></strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Development Story</h2>Heyo 🙂 Suu here.<br><br>I'm a nerd from switzerland.<br><br>I love gaming ever since, so... I decided to create my own little game (well... now it's no more little tho) - Working on Traveler since some years now.<br>It is inspired by the game \"Uru\" - an old game about traveling to different worlds, solving puzzles to go on.<br>And since I'm a really big fan of RPG's, I thought I could combine the fighting-stuff with the puzzle-stuff and well.... That happened. 🙂<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >What is the game about?</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Traveler contains right now 9 (*1) different themed worlds you are able to explore by your own<br></li><li> Traveler is an open world game with the focus on exploring and solving quests<br></li><li> Traveler is an rpg game<br></li><li> Key elements of traveler are magic, quests, world bosses and exploration goals</li></ul><br>*1: Please refer to the early access section to see our plans",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>Traveler</u></strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Development Story</h2>Heyo 🙂 Suu here.<br><br>I'm a nerd from switzerland.<br><br>I love gaming ever since, so... I decided to create my own little game (well... now it's no more little tho) - Working on Traveler since some years now.<br>It is inspired by the game \"Uru\" - an old game about traveling to different worlds, solving puzzles to go on.<br>And since I'm a really big fan of RPG's, I thought I could combine the fighting-stuff with the puzzle-stuff and well.... That happened. 🙂<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >What is the game about?</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Traveler contains right now 9 (*1) different themed worlds you are able to explore by your own<br></li><li> Traveler is an open world game with the focus on exploring and solving quests<br></li><li> Traveler is an rpg game<br></li><li> Key elements of traveler are magic, quests, world bosses and exploration goals</li></ul><br>*1: Please refer to the early access section to see our plans",
